11 (1) THE MUNICIPAL CORPORATION IN WHICH THE MULTIFAMILY
12 DWELLING UNIT IS LOCATED, IF ANY; AND
13 (2) THE MEMBERS OF THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY AND LOCAL ELECTED
